ðŸ“Œ Overview
This Power BI dashboard provides a comprehensive analysis of a financial institutionâ€™s lending operations using real-world-style loan data. The dashboard offers insights into loan performance, customer behavior, risk categorization, and month-over-month (MoM) and month-to-date (MTD) metrics using advanced DAX and custom visualizations.

